    Scope and Contents
The Academic Affairs Center for Legal Studies File (1977-86), contains the Center's Annual Report (1977-78), and published research studies including "Juvenile Diversion in Illinois (1980), "Abuse &amp; Neglect of the Elderly (1981),  and "The Springfield Area Dispute Resolution Center" (1982).  The file also contains papers for  the conference "Crossroads" (1980),  the training manual  "Child Abuse: The Legal Perspective" (1979),  and a series of brochures entitled "Your Rights Under  the Law" (1984-86).  
  
